dcterms:description: A reinforcement learning environment where the goal is to drive a car up a hill. The car starts at the bottom of a valley and must learn to accelerate to reach the flag at the top of the hill.
dcterms:title: Mountain Car

dcterms:description: A reinforcement learning environment where the goal is to balance a two-link robotic arm. The objective is to keep the end of the arm upright by applying forces to the joints.
dcterms:title: Acrobot

dcterms:description: A reinforcement learning environment where the goal is to balance a pole on a cart. The cart can move left or right to keep the pole upright.
dcterms:title: Cartpole
